## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="58f3c-104">存留期受管理實體未繫結的.NET 物件，表示其存留期。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="58f3c-104">The lifetime of a managed entity is not bound to the lifetime of the .NET object representing it.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="58f3c-105">提供者可用來建立相對應的受管理實體的新執行個體標示了這個屬性的方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="58f3c-105">The provider can use the method marked with this attribute to create a new instance of the corresponding managed entity.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="58f3c-106">方法參數應該有相同的名稱和型別做為類別繫結的建構函式的參數。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="58f3c-106">The method parameters should have the same name and type as the parameters of the class binding constructor.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="58f3c-107">使用這個屬性的儲存機制中的 WMI 類別的登錄沒有任何影響。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="58f3c-107">Use of this attribute does not have any affect on registration of the WMI class in the repository.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="58f3c-108">它只會用於在執行階段。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="58f3c-108">It is only used at runtime.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="58f3c-109">下列範例會示範如何使用 ManagementCreate 屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="58f3c-109">The following example demonstrates how to use the ManagementCreate attribute.</span></span>  
  
```  
[ManagementEntity]  
public class ProcessInstance  
{  
     [ManagementKey]  
     public int Id;   
  
     [ManagementCreate]  
     public ProcessInstance StartProcess(string cmdLine)  
     {  
        ProcessInstance newProcess = new ProcessInstance(cmdLine);  
        newProcess.Start();  
        return newProcess;  
     }  
}  
```
